headline: Paramount (PSKY) Stock Trades Down, Here Is Why
summary: Shares of multinational media and entertainment corporation Paramount (NASDAQ:PARA) fell 4.1% in the afternoon session after continued weakness as reports surfaced that the newly merged company with Skydance is preparing for a significant wave of layoffs.
